channel.title: Searching for a SuperLeet Development Team
channel.description:
[center]Hello I would first like to welcome you to my Recruitment page, in here I will be describing for you what exactly I am looking for, and what I am trying to accomplish.[/center] [hr] [center]BASE: Advanced '[size=18pt]Project Insanity[/size]'. [PI] What skills I am looking for; an advanced GFX Designer. an advanced Graphic Designer. an Expert Java Programmer.
I probably sound crazy asking for these skills because there what everybody needs, but I am vouched on becoming the Best of the Best,. I have spent to much Time, Money, and Effort to just give up at any time. I keep on pushing until I achieve what I need or even want.
I Want to be the Best of the Best, I Need to be the Best of the Best, So I will be the BEST of the Best.
Why is that you may ask? Because I take Pride in my work, and accomplishing things on my own,..... I Try. [/center]

item.title: Searching for a SuperLeet Development Team
item.dc:creator: @Da_Vein Da Vein
item.description:
@Da_Vein wrote:

[quote=“The Web Guy, post:4, topic:462115”][quote author=Da Vein link=topic=565072.msg4112286#msg4112286 date=1348631772]
Because I take Pride in my work, and accomplishing things on my own,… I Try.
[/quote]

So… Is this why you’re getting developers for every area? To do the work for you? :|[/quote]No, I don’t need them, it would just make things go smoother. To help put together good ideas and make them happen. Like I have some crazy good ideas, i’m just not 100% on how to make it happen. And with the GFX Designer, well he/she’s on there own, I know nothing about that shiznits. And I would LIKE a good Graphic designer…
@Scarecrows - I am the Best already. My server will be posted on New Years, and everyone will see.
